<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Re:View - 오답 분석 리포트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <style>
        .analysis-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .feedback-card { background: #fff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 5px solid #007bff; margin-bottom: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .stat-highlight { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; }
        .chart-container { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .analysis-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">Re:View</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/board">게시판</a>
                <a href="/analysis" style="font-weight: bold; color: #007bff;">분석</a>
                <a href="/profile">마이페이지</a>
                <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <header style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
            <h1>오답 분석 리포트</h1>
            <p style="color: #666;">사용자 <strong><%= user.username %></strong>님의 학습 데이터를 분석한 결과입니다.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="val"><%= totalCount %></span>
                <span class="lbl">누적 오답 수</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="val"><%= weeklyCount %></span>
                <span class="lbl">최근 7일 작성</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="analysis-grid">
            <div class="chart-container">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">틀린 원인 분석</h3>
                <% if (typeStats.length > 0) { %>
                    <canvas id="typeChart"></canvas>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p style="text-align: center; color: #999; padding: 50px;">데이터가 부족하여 차트를 표시할 수 없습니다.</p>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="feedback-section">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">맞춤형 피드백</h3>
                <% feedbacks.forEach(msg => { %>
                    <div class="feedback-card">
                        <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;"><%= msg %></p>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
                <% if (feedbacks.length === 0) { %>
                    <p style="color: #999;">분석된 피드백이 없습니다.</p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 50px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="/write" class="btn btn-primary">오답 더 기록하러 가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        <% if (typeStats.length > 0) { %>
        const ctx = document.getElementById('typeChart').getContext('2d');
        new Chart(ctx, {
            type: 'doughnut',
            data: {
                labels: <%- JSON.stringify(typeStats.map(s => s.name)) %>,
                datasets: [{
                    data: <%- JSON.stringify(typeStats.map(s => s.count)) %>,
                    backgroundColor: [
                        '#ff6384', '#36a2eb', '#cc65fe', '#ffce56', '#4bc0c0', '#9966ff'
                    ],
                    borderWidth: 1
                }]
            },
            options: {
                responsive: true,
                plugins: {
                    legend: { position: 'bottom' }
                }
            }
        });
        <% } %>
    </script>
</body>
</html>
